    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/735762d6a14a3f7ee54d9cf371199b64.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=72 /></span>当你在你日常最喜欢去的沙滩上醒来时，和你疏远多年的儿时玩伴正站在你身边。你能想起的最后一幕，就是自己也因为肆虐全世界的疾病而痛苦不已，然后失去了意识。你和其他三位同伴如何生存下去？这世界是否还有其他幸存者？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你努力求生时，你发现了更多的未解之谜……也许真相将会被你揭开面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/ac7b73600119eaebccc36021f103275f.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=73 /></span>和其他幸存者度过每一天，深入了解他们。在这部以故事驱动的视觉小说中，你将和他们一起协作揭开世界的真相，并发展成为更亲密的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/405c454e256a6c3480d881321360380e.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/f799582601f6537ff0f5c81bbd122dbf.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/6184796af6bbecd5dbf791c14b976787.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377410/extras/a96a4ea0f96926596e62adefdc96b9e0.avif?t=1749034330\" width=616 height=73 /></span><strong>浪漫又神秘的视觉小说</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他幸存者交谈，增进好感，创造羁绊……并找出真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精美手绘插图</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的插图让每一个角色都栩栩如生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种结局等待开启</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的浪漫故事将如何发展？你能否与心爱之人发掘谜团真相？还是当阻碍出现时，你们的羁绊将就此断绝？</p>",
